<h2> Definition </h2>

<p>When expressing the fact that an object is made from a raw material, the latter is marked with
<strong>@HI{{kara}}</strong>. If it is clearly visible that the object is made from that raw material, then
<strong>@HI{{de}}</strong> is preferred instead.
</p>

