  </td> </tr>
  <tr class="en"> <td>
      Beer is made from barley.
  </td> </tr>
  <tr class="jp"> <td>
      @HI{{@KJ{{once*upon*a*time day^book}}no@KJ{{house}}ha @KJ{{tree}}<strong>de</strong>
      @KJ{{create}}raremashita.}}
  </td> </tr>
  <tr class="en"> <td>
      Japanese houses were made of wood in the past.
  </td> </tr>
</table>
